title: Haydn - The Complete Symphonies
description:
Music : Classical : Lossless



This is a compilation of Joseph Haydn's complete symphonies as performed by the Austro-Hungarian Haydn Orchestra with Adam Fischer as conductor.

These performances are all in DDD and were recorded at the Esterhazy Palace in Eisenstadt at Haydn's very own concert hall, the Haydnsaal (Haydn was Kapellmeister to the Esterhazy princes). 

Performances were begun in 1987 and were not completed until 2001.



Contained in this torrent are:
Symphonies No.1-104
Symphony "A"
Symphony "B"
Sinfonia Concertante in B flat major.



All files were ripped in secure mode to FLAC lossless format.
